  "text": "Septic shock is an infection-based disease entity. It is not a singular, homogenous disease in the traditional sense. [CITATION_1] To investigate the molecular mechanism of pediatric septic shock is critically important for the diagnosis, treatment, and prognosis. The expression profiling by microarray can provide information about the expression differences of thousands of genes in human genome. In this study, we used it to predict ",
